{"tid":122324,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"紅底校長要求我地撐七警","createTime":"2017-02-16T02:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T05:53:26.000Z","uid":42492,"like":0,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6de66a7113a5ba451208bf855a7e0bad7ca4c424","tid":122324,"uid":42492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"小弟今年第一年做老師，入到去先知間野超紅底，今日校長send左封咁既野黎<br />\n<br />\n七警求情信<br />\n***********<br />\n<br />\n另, 有關七警案, 不同人士有不同看法。有人認為，嚴懲七警可彰顯香港的公義，因私刑實在不可鼓勵，必須嚴懲（正如老師不可以打學生一樣）。但亦有人認為，七警是在對方以「淋尿」的方法挑釁而作出不理智行為，雖做錯但寄予同情。<br />\n<br />\n以下是一些其他學校校長傳來的訊息，倘同事認為合適，可以考慮採取相應行動（今天十二時前)，謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n一人一電郵 實名聯署 <br />\n要求法官輕判七警<br />\n<br />\n電郵地址:<br />\ninfo@jpoa.com.hk<br />\n(香港警察隊員佐級協會)<br />\n或<br />\ninfo@chkp.org<br />\n(愛護香港力量)<br />\n<br />\n香港警察隊員佐級協會，將接收全部聯署電郵轉達市民支持，並轉交七位警務人員代表律師，謝謝你的支持。<br />\n<br />\n編者的話:<br />\n各位香港市民朋友，香港警隊作為治安前線，在經歷佔中及社會動亂後，受到沉重壓力，犯了一些非理性行為，應被我等市民能理解及得到體諒，本人請求各位聯署，請求法官輕判七位警務人員，使社會能早日從回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n(實名電郵樣本參考)<br />\n<br />\n請求信<br />\n<br />\n致 區域法院法官閣下<br />\n<br />\n香港警隊作為治安前線，在經歷佔中及社會動亂後，受到沉重壓力，犯了一些非理性行為，是我等市民所能理解及體諒，本人請求法官輕判七位警務人員，使社會能早日從回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n聯署人(             )<br />\n2017年2月16日<br />\n<br />\n#一人一電郵要求輕判七警 <br />\n#請盡量廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c50a2e50a544050bc2a2ac1907c4a3e9f2ddd7","tid":122324,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"推上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f259198ff535cdcd097b19becf8b744e86e43626","tid":122324,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"咩學校又唔講<br />\n叫人點撐你呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b666e5d0fa42f059eac1a8fde2850d8cb60ffd38","tid":122324,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩學校又唔講<br />\n叫人點撐你呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講咗樓主實冇工返，你養？"},{"pid":"171cb690d8b21236880cf4a366ed0be685fcce66","tid":122324,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a79874fa09a85015b87bb1cbec519619c22de927","tid":122324,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩學校又唔講<br />\n叫人點撐你呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講咗樓主實冇工返，你養？</blockquote><br />\n連學校都唔知係邊間<br />\n俾你推到上報又有乜用呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb293706694debd6230017e430f83b788fbaa9b","tid":122324,"uid":7966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:35:54.000Z","msg":"將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fc3c1048714c54a4af0d38b83a0bc90a14ea45","tid":122324,"uid":61818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"巴打開名 公審個校長  搞到佢工都無得做"},{"pid":"22ea7cc25a8ff201ea2ef507b686abc80a28058d","tid":122324,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a1f07c3cacf86c155eef667807f0463e8dac63","tid":122324,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"樓主蠢左 爆自己第一日做老師 個校長盲既都知你係邊個啦 就算你唔爆校名 比佢知依個post都係大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e16cbab28cab5d4dd674fcdcc9731763c85a65","tid":122324,